        <updateDate>2025-11-13T21:18:51Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Syria Terrorism Threat Assessment Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill requires the Department of Homeland Security to provide Congress with an assessment of terrorist threats to the United States posed by individuals in Syria affiliated with either a foreign terrorist organization or a specially designated global terrorist organization.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
